<h2>AI 相关</h2>

<p>1、<a href="https://github.com/features/copilot/cli">GitHub Copilot CLI</a></p>

<p><img src="https://cdn.beekka.com/blogimg/asset/202509/bg2025092705.webp" alt="" title="" /></p>

